  "text": "Because this study happened to include only females, a follow-up study used the same protocol to investigate EFTs' generalizability to different demographic groups. It enrolled 1 group of students pursuing a degree in sports science (predominantly male and younger) and a second group with a major in complementary medicine (predominantly female and older). The students enrolled in the sports science cohort were younger by an average of 17 years. The study found no differences in anxiety reduction on the basis of either sex or age [CITATION_1] .",
